{"tid":1592923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這個就係林鄭既目的？讓香港充滿仇恨及反政府","createTime":"2019-09-24T23:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:14:06.000Z","uid":117649,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d15b77f4d41a1c11178446234f0b66f30783e784","tid":1592923,"uid":117649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:46:02.000Z","msg":"中共搞掂完西藏及新疆後，終於輪到香港，佢地容不下一絲無法掌握的領土，開始對香港開刀。<br />\n<br />\nStandard: The Chief Executive Carrie Lam Cheng Yuet-ngor said she finds it &quot;quite remarkable&quot; by international standards that there have been no deaths yet as a result of the anti-government protests that are now into their fourth month, RTHK reports. （英文版本原文）<br />\n<br />\n翻譯年糕:以國際標準，四個月的反政府活動未造成死亡，佢覺得「相當了不起」<br />\n<br />\nlink： <a href=\"http://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking-news.php?id=134936&amp;story_id=134936&amp;d_str=20190924&amp;sid=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandard.com.hk%2Fbreaking-news.php%3Fid%3D134936%26story_id%3D134936%26d_str%3D20190924%26sid%3D4&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=89aef549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking-news.php?id=134936&amp;story_id=134936&amp;d_str=20190924&amp;sid=4</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道香港好重要，因為有錢，無論外國還是國內的，所以要全面統治香港，首先要破壞佢，反政府主義係一個相當好既方法。<br />\n<br />\n諗多一層，整個運動政府既行動好模糊，主要都係由警出來控制，好似就係製造對立，製造反政府主義，政府沒有高層出來安撫，甚至火上加油，推啲爭議大的政策，光明正大咁派遣鄉黑勢力，製造不信任及不安全，撕裂成個社會。<br />\n<br />\n中共一直都想從各方面控制香港產業，用內地輸電去取代中電港燈，威逼國泰導致高層機長離職，控制港鐵等等，仲有再早些既匯豐，都顯示中共無時無刻想侵吞香港。香港既書局，工程大部分都已經比中共把持，淡水也是由廣東供應。<br />\n<br />\n香港不再穩定，遊行示威活動，被營造成混亂的表象，令到外國投資者卻步，甚至離開，香港的金融地位也逐漸削減，學生無法安心投入學習研究，非大陸旅客不敢來香港，人心恍惚，停滯，無論係社會，民生，政策，教育還是商業。<br />\n<br />\n當這場運動繼續落去，對立不斷加深，直接的衝突死亡是好可能出現，例如而家藍絲用刀斬人，會唔會有無法忍受者做出同樣既事情，比中共有藉口進入香港市面，以打擊恐怖襲擊的名義，然後將香港人關在一個個「再教育營」內。<br />\n<br />\n好亂<br />\n<br />\n未完待續<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"2e7ee4be8eb60aa4b9aaf94939ac485c5a7c4dbb","tid":1592923,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"2e05075040b3ea042480ff706a0384c12a34aa59","tid":1592923,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:47:08.000Z","msg":"睇下邊個蝕啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2062d934985b0ebfccc8345fc67a4cd0390bad55","tid":1592923,"uid":108571,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:48:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪一直講緊林奠先係真正漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係CIA 派黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a431986158992037ee9fd2b732ed03433fb47922","tid":1592923,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2062d934985b0ebfccc8345fc67a4cd0390bad55","tid":1592923,"uid":108571,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:48:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪一直講緊林奠先係真正漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係CIA 派黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:49:19.000Z","msg":"